name: Kabuhayang Swak na Swak
overview: Kabuhayang Swak na Swak is an entrepreneurial and informative show produced by Bayan Productions, Inc. which airs weekend mornings on ABS-CBN. The program features ways, means and techniques of how to start, setting up and maintaining a certain business. It is currently presented by Bobby Yan, with the special participation of Dimples Romana and airs every Saturday and Sunday at 7:00 a.m..
